quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  61,1,"Sbuccuâen Öebbi, kra illan deg igenwan, akked kra illan di tmurt. Neppa d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab."
  61,2,"A wid iumnen! Acimi id teqqaôem ayen ur txeddmem?"
  61,3,"D lâaô meqqwôen, ar Öebbi, ma teqqaôem ayen ur txeddmem."
  61,4,"Ih, Öebbi Iêemmel wid ipna$en deg ubrid iS, d ûûef, nitni, amzun d lebni, iéevêen."
  61,5,"Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: ""a yagdud iw! Acimi la yi teîîuôum, u ni$ teéôam nek d amazan n Öebbi $uôwen""? Mi ff$en i ubrid, Öebbi Issuffe$ i ubrid ulawen nnsen. Öebbi ur Inehhu ara agdud iballa$en."
  61,6,"Mi inna Âisa, mmi s n Meryem: ""A yAt Isôail! Nek d amazan n Öebbi $uôwen, ad tebbte$ ayen iyi d izwaren n Tuôa. U a kwen beccôe$ s Umazan ara d iasen, deffir i, ism is Aêmed"". Mi ten id iusa s ubeggen, nnan: ""wagi d ssêur n ûûeê""."
  61,7,"Anwa idensen sennig win id igren tikerkas af Öebbi, u neppa ipwanced ar wannuz? Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas."
  61,8,"B$an ad ssexsin tafat n Öebbi, s imawen nnsen. Öebbi ad Itim tafat iS, di nneqwma ijehliyen."
  61,9,"D Neppa id Iuznen Amazan iS, s nnhaya, d ddin n tidep, iwakken a t issifrir f ddin meôôa, di nneqwma ijehliyen."
  61,10,"A wid iumnen! Ma d awen Mle$ ssuq ara kwen isellken seg uâaqeb aqeôêan?"
  61,11,"Amnet s Öebbi akked Umazan iS. Nna$et deg ubrid n Öebbi s wayla nnwen, u s yiman nnwen; ppif akka i kunwi, lemmer tessinem."
  61,12,"Ad awen Isemmeê ibekkaven nnwen; a kwen Issekcem ar leonanat degsen isaffen ppazzalen, tinezdu$in igerzen, di leonanat n Âaden; d wagi ay d rrbeê ameqwôaêan."
  61,13,"Ayen têemmlem nniven: afus s$uô Öebbi akked l$elb aqôib. Ssefôeê lmumnin."
  61,14,"A wid iumnen! Illit d iwiziwen n Öebbi, akken inna Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, i inmahalen is: ""anwi ay d iwiziwen iw ar Öebbi""? Nnan d inmahalen: ""nekwni d iwiziwen n Öebbi"". Tumen terbaât, tejhel terbaât, n At Isôail. Nefka afus i wid iumnen, mgal icenga nnsen, d$a rebêen."
